## Quick Start (Local vs Public)

### 1. Local Mode (Full Access)
Process your library and private chats with full visibility:
```bash
python scan.py --dir "C:/path/to/library"
```

### 2. Static Mode (Public Exhibit)
Generate the redacted data for GitHub Pages:
```bash
python scan.py --static
```

